=== 堵塞人行道和盲道 ===
[[File:20180311街角损坏的ofo单车.jpg|thumb]]在获得了巨额投资之后，ofo的运营采用了车海战术，在多地加大了投放力度<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/143359281_454028|title=ofo被10余个城市禁止投放因管理能力弱|accessdate=2017-05-25|date=2017-08-11|publisher=搜狐|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216034416/http://www.sohu.com/a/143359281_454028|archive-date=2017-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但由于管理未能跟进，且ofo自行车没有桩基或电子围栏限制，自行车过多挤占人行道、盲道等公共空间，随意停放的ofo单车给盲人以及需要靠轮椅行动的残疾人士带来巨大危险与困难{{r|visu|disa}}，导致行人“找路难”，交通违规现象增加，引起了民众不满<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mxwz.com/pingyi/py_view.aspx?ID=794385 |title=OFO违规投放，是可忍孰不可忍！ |accessdate= |date= |publisher=政民互动群众工作站 |language=zh |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215221356/http://www.mxwz.com/pingyi/py_view.aspx?ID=794385 |archive-date=2017-12-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和管理部门的重视。ofo在部分城市被清退<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1569288678170899&wfr=spider&for=pc|title=多家权威媒体报道ofo被15城清退|accessdate=|date=|publisher=百度|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215221323/http://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1569288678170899&wfr=spider&for=pc|archive-date=2017-12-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.csdn.net/junminorg/article/details/73087794|title=共享单车回收难ofo垃圾成山共享单车该如何管理？|date=2017-06-12|publisher=CSDN|access-date=2017-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225203006/http://blog.csdn.net/junminorg/article/details/73087794|archive-date=2017-12-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>北京、上海、深圳、杭州等地相继出台《共享单车指导意见》，进一步限制其自行车尤其是机械锁自行车的投放。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.labour-daily.cn/ldb/node13/node15/u1ai365201.html|title=上海共享单车发展指导意见出台|accessdate=|date=|publisher=劳动报|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215163759/http://www.labour-daily.cn/ldb/node13/node15/u1ai365201.html|archive-date=2017-12-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.66163.com/2017-04-24/1183544.shtml|title=即使没有出台规范意见ofo召回车辆也是理所应当|accessdate=|date=|publisher=福建之窗|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215163753/http://news.66163.com/2017-04-24/1183544.shtml|archive-date=2017-12-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>ofo之類共享单车被投放到大中城市后，城市交通违规现象增加，占用机动车道的现象比比皆是。斑马线上骑行、逆行和占用机动车道成为ofo等共享单车交通违法的“三宗罪”。{{r|中国网}}

由于ofo等共享单车的混乱停放造成不便，并且ofo的运营管理与车辆总数不相匹配<ref>{{cite web|title=用时方便骑完一扔,共享单车谁来安放?|url=https://m.huanqiu.com/r/MV8wXzExMDgzMjkyXzkwXzE1MDE4ODA2NTM=|website=环球网|access-date=2018-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217112438/https://m.huanqiu.com/r/MV8wXzExMDgzMjkyXzkwXzE1MDE4ODA2NTM=|archive-date=2019-02-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而造成物业管理人员的额外负担。在其投放的城市，有部分市政设施、景区、机关单位和小区禁止共享单车进入大门。<ref>{{cite web|title=小区物业纷纷下“禁令”禁止共享单车进小区，合理吗|url=http://zjnews.zjol.com.cn/zjnews/hznews/201707/t20170713_4552232.shtml|website=浙江新闻|access-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224214106/http://zjnews.zjol.com.cn/zjnews/hznews/201707/t20170713_4552232.shtml|archive-date=2017-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web|title=高校禁止共享单车入内是否应该|url=http://p.baidu.com/question/23fb6162636438623836340200|access-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224214256/http://p.baidu.com/question/23fb6162636438623836340200|archive-date=2017-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=“共享单车”or“共享围城”？多地已禁止进公共区域|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2017-05-09/doc-ifyexxhw2855881.shtml|website=新浪科技|access-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170509023401/http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2017-05-09/doc-ifyexxhw2855881.shtml|archive-date=2017-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=五一假期出游，多个景区禁止共享单车进入|url=http://news.cctv.com/2017/05/01/ARTI9WVuqWqSfA5BZoANWhok170501.shtml|work=CCTV|access-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225034853/http://news.cctv.com/2017/05/01/ARTI9WVuqWqSfA5BZoANWhok170501.shtml|archive-date=2017-12-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>

ofo投入国外后，由于社会负面效应，而遭到一些国外城市社区反感，也有被许多城市清退{{r|fal}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/dallas-city-council/2018/01/20/disabled-rent-bikes-annoyance-violate-ada|title=For disabled people, rent-a-bikes are more than an annoyance, but do they violate the ADA? | Dallas City Council|accessdate=2018-11-21|date=2018-01-20|publisher=Dallas News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314140201/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/dallas-city-council/2018/01/20/disabled-rent-bikes-annoyance-violate-ada|archive-date=2018-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/highland-park/2018/01/05/highland-parks-new-bike-share-law-town-round-auction-urban-litter|title=Highland Park's new bike-share law lets town round up and auction off 'urban litter' | Highland Park|accessdate=2018-11-21|date=|publisher=Dallas News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817060122/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/highland-park/2018/01/05/highland-parks-new-bike-share-law-town-round-auction-urban-litter|archive-date=2018-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasobserver.com/news/dallas-bike-share-ultimatum-clean-up-bike-litter-or-the-city-will-10278430|title=Dallas Bike Share Ultimatum: Clean Up Bike Litter or the City Will|accessdate=2018-11-21|author=Stephen Young|date=2018-01-19|publisher=Dallas Observer|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817092335/https://www.dallasobserver.com/news/dallas-bike-share-ultimatum-clean-up-bike-litter-or-the-city-will-10278430|archive-date=2018-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{r|glob}}。
=== 产生废弃车辆 ===
[[File:A_shared_bicycle_in_the_grass.jpg|200px]]
由于ofo单车的價格低廉，以及早期的ofo自行车均采用固定密码的机械锁，易被破解和损坏且无法被监控到。这使得ofo的损坏、丢失率远高于其他品牌共享单车<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinaz.com/news/2017/0301/666068.shtml|title=腾讯共享单车报告：ofo车辆故障率接近40% 或拖累融资|date=2017-03-01|publisher=站长之家|access-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922194032/http://www.chinaz.com/news/2017/0301/666068.shtml|archive-date=2017-09-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，“僵尸车”、“报废车”在城市街头随处可见。如何处置这些垃圾成山的“街头废钢”成为社会的一个新问题。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.labour-daily.cn/ldb/node41/node2151/20170713/n62314/n62326/u1ai344332.html|title=30万吨“街头废铁”该何去何从？|date=2017-07-12|publisher=劳动报|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224054155/http://b2b.toocle.com/detail--6405211.html|archivedate=2017-12-24|deadurl=yes|access-date=2017-12-25}}</ref>{{r|负面}}

由于ofo的高损坏率事实，“ofo”的读音又类似于英文Awful，坊间流传有“Awful”的绰号。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.jianshu.com/p/1edd1506475b|title=道不同，不相怼|access-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314123639/https://www.jianshu.com/p/1edd1506475b|archive-date=2018-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 車鎖不嚴 ===
ofo的车锁被曝不付费就可以“容易打开”，甚至儿童都可以轻易打开。2017年3月26日，一位未满12周岁的上海儿童因骑ofo单车被大客车碾压死亡，引发社会关注。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://tech.gmw.cn/2017-03/28/content_24075220.htm|title=儿童骑ofo不幸殒命ofo车锁破解技巧小学生中流传|date=2017-03-28|publisher=新闻晨报|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180320030014/http://tech.gmw.cn/2017-03/28/content_24075220.htm|archivedate=2018-03-20|accessdate=2017-07-13}}</ref>後ofo被判賠償兒童家屬6.7萬餘元<ref>{{cite news |title=全国首例未满12岁男孩骑ofo车祸身亡巨额索赔案宣判：被告赔偿6.7万余元 |url=http://app.cctv.com/special/cportal/detail/arti/index.html?id=Arti9ykkTa5S1NzDA7tvAjDc200612&fromapp=cctvnews&version=727 |access-date=2020-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612172837/http://app.cctv.com/special/cportal/detail/arti/index.html?id=Arti9ykkTa5S1NzDA7tvAjDc200612&fromapp=cctvnews&version=727 |archive-date=2020-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

为了减少损坏率和机械锁破解问题，ofo将原有自行车上的机械锁更换为电子锁，同时增设警告标志。然而电子锁也被曝出“并不智能”，且寿命较短<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.zol.com.cn/644/6442237.html|title=ofo究竟是不是智能锁？拆开大吃一惊|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181020033129/http://news.zol.com.cn/644/6442237.html|archive-date=2018-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而用户却并不买账，认为ofo新车骑行费劲笨重难骑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/156761371_99912208|title=为什么摩拜越来越轻 ofo小黄车却越来越重越难骑|publisher=搜狐|access-date=2017-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226130320/http://www.sohu.com/a/156761371_99912208|archive-date=2017-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://tech.ifeng.com/a/20170712/44651119_0.shtml|title=ofo电子锁小黄车被用户吐槽:不是一般的难骑|date=2017-07-12|publisher=凤凰网|access-date=2017-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226130309/http://tech.ifeng.com/a/20170712/44651119_0.shtml|archive-date=2017-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

